description.en: CheChoin is a reflection token inspired by the legend of Ernest “Che” Chevara. The idea behind the project is to create a token to give back to the people (in this case to the holders). $CheCoin offers an innovative protocol in its contract : Rewards paid in BNB. Thanks to the auto-claim feature, you just have to hold $CheCoin to receive every hour BNB dividends. Hold $CheCoin and get paid on every transaction.
